works.description:
Three photographs of Natalia Villaveces: 

kneeling in front of a fan, kneeling on a couch/chair with a red shawl,
and  
standing in front of a fan wit a light green scarf. At least one of these 

photos appeared in the March 2003 issue of Playboy in an article  
titled "Latin TV Stars."
PLEASE NOTE: The group photo at the top of the page, which has a copyright
 
notice for a Suze Randall, is NOT part of this DMCA notice. Only the three
 
photos of Ms. Villaveces.
